ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectGeneral Preferential Tariff and Least Developed Country Tariff Rules of Origin Regulations
PrecisGENERAL PREFERENTIAL TARIFF AND LEAST DEVELOPED COUNTRY TARIFF RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS in order to amend the current regulations so that products imported from least developed countries qualify for duty-free treatment under the LDCT, effective January 1, 2015.
